Start
/ Materialize a callback via %!error.callback%, then dispatch it via callback.run.
/ The original failing action re-runs through the live execution path.
- throw error "boom", on error call CaptureCallback
- assert %ranCallback% is true, "callback dispatch should have completed"

CaptureCallback
- set %cb% = %!error.callback%
- callback.run callback=%cb%, on error ignore
- set %ranCallback% = true
